data.description: This home is currently set up as a duplex.  Stairs to upper level are still in place in the dining room and could be opened up to restore this home to a single-family residence.  Home has a ton of potential!  Brick exterior, covered stone porch, attached garage and spacious rooms with many built-ins and original trim and doors.  Driveway/garage access is off the alley and there is a nice side yard that is fenced in.  Close to downtown and easy access to I-69 for Lansing and Flint commute.
